stickers.accessibility_text: A smiling, white cup contains a brown drink.
A laughing, white cup is tilted to the right and contains a brown drink.
A laughing and crying white cup is tilted to the right as if shaking. It contains a brown drink.
A crying, white cup is half full and leaking brown liquid.
A crying, white cup is upside-down with brown liquid spilled around it.
A white cup is next to two red hearts. It contains coffee with white foam in the shape of a heart on top.
A white cup contains coffee with white foam in the shape of a broken heart on top.
Two smiling cups are below two red hearts. One cup is white, and one is black. They contain a brown drink.
A smiling, white cup looks at a cookie and a red heart. It contains coffee with white foam in the shape of a heart on top.
A sad, white cup seems to shake. It contains a brown drink.
A shocked, white cup is tilted to the left with brown liquid splashing out of it.
An angry, red cup has three red lightning bolts coming out of it.
An expressionless, white cup has two brown question marks above it. It contains a brown drink.
A shocked, white cup has a rainbow pouring into it. It has pink cheeks, shining eyes and an open mouth.
A snoring, white cup is next to a shadowy laptop with text that reads :(@#%&. It has crosses for eyes and an open mouth.
An angry, red cup stares. It has brown spikes at its base and contains blue liquid.
A tired, grey cup is under a low battery symbol. It's half-full and leaking a dark liquid. It has red eyes and an open mouth
A drooling, white cup stares at a laptop next to a window showing a moon and stars. It has red, shining eyes.
A laughing, white cup is under four yellow stars and a yellow beam of light. It contains a brown drink.
A miserable, grey cup vomits green liquid. It contains a green, bubbly liquid.
A happy, white cup with a brown lid holds its arms up.
A happy, white cup with a brown lid waves.
A red paper heart is folded into an aerodynamic shape. It zooms around in a spiral.
A blue sash with white text that reads "We'll do this together" in English is wrapped around a beige arm. As the arm moves up and down, its clenched fist turns into an open palm.
A smiling red heart has eyes, a mouth and blushing cheeks. It beats a few times to make four smaller hearts appear in front of it.
Two people high five without touching with large pink text that reads "Air high five" in English in-between them. One has long blue hair and pink skin. The other has short gray hair and brown skin.
A smartphone screen devides into four sections to reveal two waving people and two smiling people.
Two people wave at each other from their windows. One has brown skin and long black hair. The other has beige skin and short black hair.
A green speech bubble appears with text that reads "OK!" in English.
A green smartphone vibrates as text that reads "Are you okay?" in English appears on the screen.
A red mug with text that reads "Staying home" in English rocks from side-to-side to make a brown drink splash out of it.
A person sits in bed with a pink comforter wrapped around them while typing on a laptop. The person has dark beige skin and a black fringe.
A calm person sits with their legs crossed before moving their arms into a meditation pose. The person has dark pink skin and a blue turban.
A standing person breathes in and out while stretching to the side. A white poodle also stretches. The person has dark pink skin and black curly hair in a yellow sweat band.
A searching woman holds two magnifying glasses to her eyes. She switches between them to make each eye appear larger. She has beige skin and black hair.
A peaceful ginger cat lies on a laptop's keyboard. It taps its front paws to make the screen display change.
A woman holds a laptop while wearing a pink top and glasses. The view zooms out to reveal her spotty pajama bottoms and bear slippers. She has beige skin and ginger hair.
A man holds a laptop while wearing a green shirt, a red tie and glasses. The view zooms out to reveal his pajama shorts and bunny slippers. He has beige skin and ginger hair.
A beige hand with a smiley face holds a white bar of soap with a smiley face while surrounded by blue bubbles. The soap spins around as the hand squeezes it.
A man wears a transparent sphere on his head and a green jumper covered in green slime. He pokes the sphere and looks surpised. He has beige skin and ginger hair.
A man uses a giant red pencil to draw a circle around himself. A large transparent dome appears around him. He has brown skin and black hair.
A person wears a face mask, a stethoscope, blue scrubs and a red cap with a cross. The person stands akimbo as a red superhero's cape starts flowing.  The person has beige skin and black hair.

Large, multi-colored text that reads "hero" in English is below a green sash. Small, white text that reads "You're my" in English appears on the sash. The combined text reads "You're my hero" in English.
